9. Install a new clip onto the drive shaft. (Refer to 03-13 DRIVE SHAFT REMOVAL/INSTALLATION Drive Shaft Installation Note.) 
10. Install the lower arm installation bolt and nut.  


Tightening torque 47- 66 N·m {4.7- 6.8 kgf·m, 34- 49 ft·lbf}  


11. Install the brake caliper component.  


Tightening torque 50- 68 N·m {5.0- 7.0 kgf·m, 37- 50 ft·lbf}  


12. Add the specified oil. (Refer to 03-14 DIFFERENTIAL OIL REPLACEMENT.) 
13. Adjust the rear wheel alignment.